cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use LegionForge in your research or build on it, please cite it using this file."

title: "LegionForge"
abstract: >
  A local-first, security-native AI agent framework built on LangGraph.
  Runs local LLMs (Ollama) or cloud APIs with a full security stack baked
  in at every layer: Guardian sidecar (7-check deterministic pipeline),
  SecureToolNode, prompt injection detection, Ed25519 tool signing,
  capability boundary enforcement, and a tool crystallization pipeline
  (LegionForge-Anneal) that converts LLM-generated actions into signed,
  sandboxed, reusable tools.

authors:
